//static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/61bnp1namql-_ac_sl1500_.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=300\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/61bnp1namql-_ac_sl1500_.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=300\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1256\" height=\"1215\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Garmin Epix Gen 2\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/61bnp1namql-_ac_sl1500_.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/61bnp1namql-_ac_sl1500_.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\n\n        \n        \n                            \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n                \n                 \n                \t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\tGarmin Epix Gen 2\n\t\t\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                                    \u003cp\u003e$485 \u003cspan\u003e$900\u003c/span\u003e Save\n                        $415 \u003c/p\u003e\n                \n                                    \u003cp\u003eWith its big, bold AMOLED display and plenty of power under the hood, the Garmin Epix Gen 2 is built for folks who take their health tracking seriously. From heart rate to sleep to stress, it keeps tabs on it all—and right now, it’s going for one of its best prices on Amazon.\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n                    \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eGarmin has been in the wearables market long enough to know what people actually need—whether you\u0026#39;re just lacing up for your first run or you\u0026#39;re the type who signs up for ultramarathons. It\u0026#39;s got a watch for every kind of grind, and the Epix Gen 2 is a real standout. It’s the kind of watch that pulls double duty—loaded with serious athletic features while still looking sleek enough to rock every day, whether you\u0026#39;re hitting the gym or heading out for the night.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eRight now, you can grab the white titanium Garmin Epix Gen 2 on Amazon for just $485, way down from its usual $900. That’s a massive $415 off, or about 46% shaved off the price tag.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"why-the-garmin-epix-gen-2-is-worth-your-money\"\u003e\n                        Why the Garmin Epix Gen 2 is worth your money\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEven though it’s not the newest kid on the block, the Garmin Epix Gen 2 has been getting steady software updates since launch, so it’s still packed with all the essentials Garmin is known for. This thing is built tough, too. It’s got a titanium bezel that looks sharp and adds protection without weighing you down, and the main body is made from fiber-reinforced polymer, meaning it\u0026#39;s light, strong, and ready to take a hit.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n    \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"ed89-4a9b-ba115f0a91ac\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/5-essential-smartwatch-features-i-cant-live-without/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/pixel-watch-feature-01.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/pixel-watch-feature-01.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/pixel-watch-feature-01.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/pixel-watch-feature-01.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/pixel-watch-feature-01.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                             